import sys

def main():
    x = float(sys.stdin.readline())
    a = int(round(x, 0))
    b = int(round(x * 10, 0)) - a * 10
    print(a, b)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

import sys

def main():
    x = float(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
    a = int(round(x))
    b = int(round(x * 10)) - a * 10
    print(a, b, sep='')

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

def main():
    x = float(input())
    a = int(x)
